    <abstract>
      <t>This memo discusses possible modifications of TLS 1.3, aimed to allow trasferring data larger than 64 Kbytes in handshake messages. One possible application for this feature is to allow using post-quantum Key Encapsulation Method that have large public key or ciphertext size (like Classic McEliece).</t>
